{"number":25,"verseCount":16,"verses":[[1,["Hearken unto the voice of the Lord your God, while I speak unto you, Emma Smith, my daughter; for verily I say unto you, all those who ",["receive",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 1:12","nt/john/1.12"],". ",["TG Sons and Daughters of God","tg/sons-and-daughters-of-god"],"."]]]," my gospel are sons and daughters in my ",["kingdom",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Kingdom of God, on Earth","tg/kingdom-of-god-on-earth"],"."]]],"."]],[2,["A revelation I give unto you concerning my will; and if thou art faithful and ",["walk",["study-note-ref","a",[["Deut. 30:16","ot/deut/30.16"],"."]]]," in the paths of ",["virtue",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Virtue","tg/virtue"],"; ",["Zion","tg/zion"],"."]]]," before me, I will preserve thy life, and thou shalt receive an ",["inheritance",["study-note-ref","c",[["D&C 52:42 (2, 5, 42)","dc-testament/dc/52.42"],"; ",["58:51 (17, 28, 51)","dc-testament/dc/58.51"],"; ",["63:48 (29, 31, 48)","dc-testament/dc/63.48"],"; ",["64:30","dc-testament/dc/64.30"],"; ",["85:7 (1–3, 7, 9)","dc-testament/dc/85.7"],"; ",["99:7","dc-testament/dc/99.7"],"; ",["101:18 (1, 6, 18)","dc-testament/dc/101.18"],"; ",["103:14 (11, 14)","dc-testament/dc/103.14"],"."]]]," in Zion."]],[3,["Behold, thy ",["sins",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 9:2","nt/matt/9.2"],"."]]]," are forgiven thee, and thou art an ",["elect",["study-note-ref","b",["IE one chosen or set apart. ",["2 Jn. 1:1 (1, 13)","nt/2-jn/1.1"],"."]]]," ",["lady",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Woman","tg/woman"],"."]]],", whom I have ",["called",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Authority","tg/authority"],"; ",["Called of God","tg/called-of-god"],"."]]],"."]],[4,[["Murmur",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Murmuring","tg/murmuring"],"."]]]," not because of the ",["things",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Knowledge","tg/knowledge"],"."]]]," which thou hast not seen, for they are ",["withheld",["study-note-ref","c",[["Luke 24:16 (10–24)","nt/luke/24.16"],"; ",["Alma 40:3","bofm/alma/40.3"],"